{"data":[{"date":"10:59 05/07","title":"Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u1ed5 2 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/real-duoc-khuyen-no-2-bom-tan-neymar-va-mbappe.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Luis Garcia cho r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe.</h2><h2>Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span>. Ph\u00eda K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo hay Karim Benzema b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Luis Garcia cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Neymar \u2013 Mbappe s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/real-duoc-khuyen-no-2-bom-tan-neymar-va-mbappe.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Garcia khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNeymar v\u00e0 Mbappe l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec Real s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cReal Madrid lu\u00f4n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 Mbappe c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 2 qu\u1ea3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d m\u00e0 Real c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u01b0ng b\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp sau khi Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 Garcia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0 t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Ronaldo t\u1eebng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 s\u0103m soi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ra sao. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3986","checkdouble":"190413"},{"date":"09:59 05/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o l\u1edbn v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 BBC c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Juventus th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro (88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho Real Madrid c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 CR7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng N\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch ra sao v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang mong ng\u00f3ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p ng\u00f4i sao Gonzalo Higuain t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh Turin. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau \u1edf Bernabeu trong 4 n\u0103m giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2009 \u2013 2013.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Higuain, anh trai Nicolas: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 h\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu em t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u nhau sau h\u01a1n 80 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i, v\u1eady n\u00ean n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Luciano Moggi c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 xong xu\u00f4i h\u1ebft c\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i, r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Real Madrid sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Munich.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ngay...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3985","checkdouble":"190405"},{"date":"09:29 05/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c c\u1ea3 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-gi-ve-qua-bom-tan-bat-ngo-fabinho-172-187241.html\" target=\"_blank\">qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Fabinho 45-50 tri\u1ec7u Euro</span> m\u1edf m\u00e0n k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Monaco.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n khi Fabinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man Utd qua c\u00e1c phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung kia n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man Utd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u1ee7a Fabinho.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghe l\u1eddi ra l\u1eddi v\u00e0o v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Monaco \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Man Utd nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Liverpool m\u1edbi nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fabinho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadn m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\">Fabinho sang Liverpool: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o MU</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Fabinho sang Liverpool qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3984","checkdouble":"190403"},{"date":"10:13 05/07","title":"Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-noi-fabinho-dang-gia-nhat-cua-chuyen-nhuong-mu-172-162081.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United \u01b0u ti\u00ean</span> chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 sau khi gi\u00fap Monaco gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fabinho \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/13/Fabinho-khong-lien-he-voi-MU-nhu-bao-chi-don-thoi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd FourFourTwo g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c anh ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Man United nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Monaco. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Monaco. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgay khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190352.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3983","checkdouble":"190409"},{"date":"10:50 05/07","title":"Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina \u2013 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea n\u1ebfm tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. H\u1ecd qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Alvaro Morata &ndash; bom t\u1ea5n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi Michy Batshuayi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bao. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Olivier Giroud, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecfi mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u01b0ng \u00fd v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina \u0111\u00e3 quay ngo\u1eaft 180 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juve, sau khi anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y CLB chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec7 Cristiano Ronaldo. T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 Higuain kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo anh trai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n &ndash; Nicolas Higuain cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c. Gonzalo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Gonzalo h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, CLB, HLV, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n nh\u1ea3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Gonzalo c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi HLV Sarri (ng\u01b0\u1eddi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea). Nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft, Sarri v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Gonzalo \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Turin v\u00e0 CLB c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Gonzalo ra \u0111i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Higuain, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ngay...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3982","checkdouble":"190411"},{"date":"07:21 05/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport Mediaset, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Chelsea chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00ec M.U b\u1ecf ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm sau ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Everton l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia. C\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Anh cung c\u1ea5p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Ramirez bi Costa Rica sa thai\" title=\"Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCosta Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd khuy\u00ean Neymar ng\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha &ldquo;\u0103n v\u1ea1&rdquo; t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd, Claudio Gentile \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u1eebng vi\u1ec7c di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Mateo Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" title=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-47-MU-quan-tam-sao-tuyen-Croatia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Mina&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Liverpool Echo, Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean PSG h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Chelsea ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 cho PSG thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3981","checkdouble":"190395"},{"date":"07:06 05/07","title":"Inter Milan \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/inter-milan-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, Sky Sport Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMatteo Darmian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU t\u1eeb Torino v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Valencia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/inter-milan-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Darmian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Darmian n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, Sky Sport Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Darmian\" title=\"Matteo Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Matteo Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Matteo Darmian, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. M.U \u0111\u00f2i 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Inter ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 15 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-189764.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Darmian</span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao M.U \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989. N\u1ebfu Inter Milan kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t Darmian v\u00e0o tay Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Darmian t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan ho\u1eb7c Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3980","checkdouble":"190390"},{"date":"21:58 04/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2018m\u00e0i s\u1eafc\u2019 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/u19-viet-nam-mai-sac-hang-cong-quyet-thang-dam-lao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U18 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec thua k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>\u00a0U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch c\u1ef1c luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Philippines 5-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 u\u1ed1n n\u1eafn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0i s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\" U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0i s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/u19-viet-nam-06-2125.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 4/7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 L\u00e0o, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 2 nh\u00f3m, m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nh\u00f3m c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, t\u1eadp b\u00e0i 4 ch\u1ed1ng 4. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00e9t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c\u00a0HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n\u00a0d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian r\u00e8n gi\u0169a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn 2 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam quy\u1ebft ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Tu\u1ea5n \u2018con\u2019 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Philippines. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Philippines c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Philippines c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi U19 L\u00e0o v\u00e0o l\u00fac 15h30 ng\u00e0y mai 5/7. Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng A l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Th\u00e1i Lan nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/thua t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3979","checkdouble":"190381"},{"date":"20:23 04/07","title":"Trang ch\u1ee7 Real ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/trang-chu-real-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-thong-tin-chieu-mo-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb PSG.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Les Bleus tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trang ch\u1ee7 Real ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trang ch\u1ee7 Real ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/tien-dao-mbappe-dung-tien-thuong-tai-world-cup-2018-de-lam-tu-thien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trang ch\u1ee7 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u2018hot\u2019 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng CLB Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y ngay sau World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n sau khi nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o AS s\u1ed1 ra ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (04/07) ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3\u00a0l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 1\u00a0trong\u00a02\u00a0c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 Neymar ho\u1eb7c Mbappe.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ch\u1ee7 Real Madrid \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec ph\u00eda Real Madrid\u00a0ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u00edt gi\u1edd qua li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Real Madrid v\u00e0 PSG cho Kylian Mbappe,\u00a0Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ecba \u0111\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn PSG hay Mbappe v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch\u00a0vi\u1ec7c lan r\u1ed9ng nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng b\u00ean li\u00ean quan.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e1c b\u1ecf tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y song s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng NHM v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Perez th\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n \u00f4ng chi b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Mbappe s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/varane-mbappe-mang-hinh-bong-cua-ro-beo-469-190173.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/varane-mbappe-mang-hinh-bong-cua-ro-beo.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/varane-mbappe-mang-hinh-bong-cua-ro-beo-469-190173.html\">Varane: Mbappe mang h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ro b\u00e9o</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Raphael Varane \u0111\u00e3 so s\u00e1nh Mbappe v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ro \u201cb\u00e9o\u201d sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-43-argentina-diem-10-cho-kylian-mbappe-421-190054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/du-am-phap-43-argentina-diem-10-cho-kylian-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-43-argentina-diem-10-cho-kylian-mbappe-421-190054.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Kylian Mbappe</span><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-argentina-461-190009.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/Antoine-Griezmann-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-argentina-461-190009.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc song nh\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ghi danh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3978","checkdouble":"190378"},{"date":"06:15 05/07","title":"Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/11/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Camp Nou.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c Antoine Griezmann g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca v\u00e0 MU quan t\u00e2m Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca v\u00e0 MU quan t\u00e2m Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Duoc-Barca-va-MU-quan-tam-Willian-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 Paulinho, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Willian \u1edf Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, anh c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng Valverde mu\u1ed1n Barca chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m\u00a01988. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Barca \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh khi ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBarca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng tin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1eeb Barca c\u1ea3. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec M.U c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Willian, Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3977","checkdouble":"190386"},{"date":"06:31 05/07","title":"Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri c\u00f9ng Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Stoke City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 19 tr\u00ean BXH Premier League. Sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 12 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong khi \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u1edbi 19. Qua \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh The Potters ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc cho ng\u00f4i sao Xherdan Shaqiri. Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Stoke. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n, t\u00ednh ra Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. \u201cT\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d, Shaqiri n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110TQG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB quan t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f4i khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady d\u00f9 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Shaqiri c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u201cch\u00fa l\u00f9n\u201d d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Stoke City \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, The Kop s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3976","checkdouble":"190387"},{"date":"06:52 05/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Sport Mediaset, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues nh\u01b0ng danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Thuong-vu-Chelsea-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia nh\u1eafm Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Sarri \u1edf Napoli. M\u00f9a 2015/16, Higuain ghi 36 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sarri.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Sport Mediaset, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Higuain. Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 16 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHiguain hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi Argentina b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018. Ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Chelsea c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u0169ng c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata s\u1eafp ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Gonzalo Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Morata</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/juventus-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea v\u00e0 Juventus trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Morata v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng cho c\u00e1c b\u00ean. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Morata c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Morata t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real Madrid, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3975","checkdouble":"190389"},{"date":"12:56 04/07","title":"B\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mikel b\u1ecb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Argentina","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/bo-tien-ve-mikel-bi-bat-coc-truoc-tran-gap-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>John Obi Mikel gi\u1ea5u HLV, v\u1eabn ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n anh nh\u1eadn tin s\u1ed1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng St. Petersburg \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Argentina, Mikel nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nigeria sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i m\u00e1y, n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi k\u1ebb m\u1edbi b\u1eaft c\u00f3c b\u1ed1 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. K\u1ebb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c \u0111e do\u1ea1 s\u1ebd gi\u1ebft b\u1ed1 t\u00f4i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin ra ngo\u00e0i&rdquo;, Mikel k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean t\u1edd Guardian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mikel b\u1ecb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mikel b\u1ecb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/a0-1488-1530638460.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mikel g\u00e1c l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i lo cho b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n v\u1edbi Mikel trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n gi\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 HLV Rohr Gernot. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi HLV b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec7n gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m xao nh\u00e3ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi HLV nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3&rdquo;, Mikel nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00e0y 26/6. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng thua 1-2 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi m\u00e0 b\u1ed1 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong tay nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c nguy hi\u1ec3m. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i lo l\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh xem li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 l\u00f2ng 180 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Nigeria. T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ebft. V\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i g\u1ea1t chuy\u1ec7n gia \u0111\u00ecnh ra kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n&rdquo;, Mikel nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMay m\u1eafn, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mikel k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00f3 h\u1eadu. B\u1ed1 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng do b\u1ecb b\u1ecdn b\u1eaft c\u00f3c tra kh\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mikel b\u1ecb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3974","checkdouble":"190359"}]}